    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "801023001",
    "title": "ぎりぎり様相論",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "模擬レースの観戦にやって来た。\r\n次のレース開始を待っていると……。",
            "enText": "I came to watch a mock race. While waiting \nfor the next race to start, I went to…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "pathId": 6044072161116950664,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "失礼。良ければ参考までに\r\n意見を聞かせて欲しいのだが。",
            "enText": "Excuse me. I'd like to ask your \nopinion, if you don't mind.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "何か困りごと？",
                    "enText": "What's your problem?",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -1753520057624763790
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -5763247419069318771
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5041036414469172583,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "ああ。天候やコースの状態、\r\n対戦相手の過去の戦績を鑑みての\n仕掛けどころの確認……。",
            "enText": "Yes. The weather, the course and your \nopponent's track record are all factors in \ndetermining where to start…",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": 8584439656036345719
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -4127460039682718477
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2824121802014113497,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "不測の事態にも対処できるような\r\n走行時における位置取りの目論見等――",
            "enText": "Contingency plans for driving \npositions, etc.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": -5085636913908924570
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 2812851028750555382
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1943453260844226090,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "このレースに臨むにあたっての準備は\r\n万全のはずだが、まだ何かある気がする……。",
            "enText": "I'm sure I'm well prepared for this \nrace, but I still feel like there's \nsomething more to it…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 8792159100894970598
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 35,
                    "pathId": -1679665204594020920
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": 3799876401743492827
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5367767135900794095,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "1％でも勝率をあげることができるならば、\r\n私はその可能性を突き詰めたい。",
            "enText": "If I can improve my odds by even 1%, I'd \nlike to explore that possibility.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -124772360712905700
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -7271845800829969609
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 3922586840356965001
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6896324398973439001,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "君にとって、レース前にすべき重要な事とは\r\nなんだ？　考えを聞かせて欲しい。",
            "enText": "What's the most important thing \nfor you to do before a race? I'd \nlike to hear your thoughts.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ぎりぎりまでトレーニング",
                    "enText": "Last minute training",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "前のレースを観察する",
                    "enText": "Observe the previous race",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 3937623024579604943
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -337790048722736417
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6073921205176502129,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "それはもちろんやったさ……\r\nいや、もっとやれと、そういう事か？",
            "enText": "I did that, of course… No, you want \nme to do more, is that it?",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": -8810905657902090195
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -5003484208660881610
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 1122254789059648983
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -484745798572270174,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "なるほど、ぎりぎりまで己を鍛える……\r\n私は思い至らなかったな……新しい見地だ。",
            "enText": "I see, train yourself to the very last… I \nhadn't thought of that … new perspective.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8766395508260909322
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 44,
                    "pathId": -8180950901863835468
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -6392830968609553096
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3813012687392577084,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "今からできることは……筋トレくらいか。\r\nよし、これからジムに行ってくるとしよう。",
            "enText": "The only thing I can do now is … strength \ntraining. Okay, I'm off to the gym now.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -3726492422973318170
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 195752827819894960
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -8894431946940359430
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1380179355786697517,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "いずれにせよ、体を温めておくというのは、\r\n無駄ではないだろうからな。",
            "enText": "In any case, it's not a waste of \ntime to keep yourself warm.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -392280170514752172
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 6637404839086098771
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 6271320946465367454
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8747582766418831759,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "斬新な観点からのアドバイス感謝する。\r\nそれでは。",
            "enText": "Thanks for the fresh perspective. \nSee you soon.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 120,
                    "pathId": -2179315262364331884
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 6701947165294230464
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8119348877712760152,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "それを忘れるわけないだろう。論じるのに、\r\n比較研究は絶対だ。過去レースの分析等――",
            "enText": "How could we forget that? In order \nto make an argument, comparative \nresearch is absolutely essential. \nAnalysis of past races…",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 4332363568454398825
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": 8746627424652003400
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1294594710152973864,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "いや……直前のコースを確認しろという事か？\r\n確かに、芝の状態等は推論に必要だが……。",
            "enText": "No. Are you asking me to check the course \njust before…? Sure, the condition of the \ngrass and other factors are necessary for \ninference, but…",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -5889759692890482755
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 2226250223259970606
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -344502946249362391
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4319212845264690751,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "しかし、多角的には視認できない。監視塔に\r\n登らせてもらうか？　いや、さすがにな……。",
            "enText": "But it's not visible from all angles. \nDo you want me to climb the watchtower? \nNo, that's a good idea…",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -7811698360284711417
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": 5191582649712539333
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 107,
                    "pathId": 8002543440274923478
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6825519004463739891,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "あ……1人でぶつぶつとすまない。\r\nともかくありがとう。検討させてもらう。",
            "enText": "Oh…1 sorry for the bumping by myself. \nAnyway, thanks. I'll look into it.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": 2457882897404882781
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 3249071872636013776
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1929979353578849451,
            "blockIdx": 16
        }
    ],
